<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>World News Today: Read the latest world news headlines, Current International breaking news world wide. In depth analysis and top news headlines world wide.</description><language>en-gb</language><lastBuildDate>2026-05-12T17:49:10+05:30</lastBuildDate><atom:link type="application/rss+xml" rel="self" href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeeds/296589292.cms"/><copyright>Copyright:(C) Tue, 12 May 2026 17:49:10 IST Bennett Coleman &amp; Co. Ltd, http://in.indiatimes.com/policyterms/1554651.cms</copyright><docs>http://syndication.indiatimes.com/</docs><image><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><url>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/507610.cms</url><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link></image><item><title><![CDATA[Nine Longest Rivers Ranked: Explainer traces Nile to Congo; shows how waterways shaped civilisations]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131030977.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Rivers, nature's vital arteries, shape landscapes and history. From the Nile's ancient reign to the Amazon's immense volume, these waterways are crucial. China's Yangtze, North America's Missouri-Mississippi, Siberia's Yenisey, and the Yellow River, cradle of civilization, highlight their global significance. Russia's Ob-Irtysh, South America's Rio de la Plata, and the deep Congo further showcase their power and reach.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/exploring-the-9-longest-rivers-in-the-world-from-the-nile-to-the-congo/articleshow/131030977.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/exploring-the-9-longest-rivers-in-the-world-from-the-nile-to-the-congo/articleshow/131030977.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-12T17:32:06+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131031797,imgsize-1714165.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[King Cobra Capitals: 10 countries where the world’s deadliest snake thrives]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131037890.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/king-cobra-capitals-10-countries-where-the-worlds-deadliest-snake-thrives/articleshow/131037890.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/king-cobra-capitals-10-countries-where-the-worlds-deadliest-snake-thrives/articleshow/131037890.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-12T17:15:21+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131038225,imgsize-1673484.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Barack Obama: "You can’t let your failures define you – you have to let them teach you. You have to let them show you what to do differently next time."]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131037633.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/quote-of-the-day-by-barack-obama-you-cant-let-your-failures-define-you-you-have-to-let-them-teach-you-you-have-to-let-them-show-you-what-to-do-differently-next-time-/articleshow/13