/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131033405,imgsize-104096.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quest for a rare bird, a landfill visit, a deadly outbreak: How Leo Schilperoord became hantavirus 'patient zero']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131027624.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A Dutch ornithologist, Leo Schilperoord, has been identified as patient zero in a deadly hantavirus outbreak on the MV Hondius cruise ship. Authorities suspect he and his wife contracted the virus from rat droppings during a birdwatching trip in Argentina. The outbreak led to multiple deaths and a global health alert.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quest-for-a-rare-bird-a-landfill-visit-a-deadly-outbreak-how-leo-schilperoord-became-hantavirus-patient-zero/articleshow/131027624.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quest-for-a-rare-bird-a-landfill-visit-a-deadly-outbreak-how-leo-schilperoord-became-hantavirus-patient-zero/articleshow/131027624.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-12T09:14:46+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131027664,imgsize-936830.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Horrifying video shows moment Frontier Airlines plane hits person on Denver runway]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131027681.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A shocking incident at Denver International Airport saw a person, who allegedly breached security, fatally struck by a departing Frontier Airlines jet. The collision ignited an engine fire, forcing an emergency evacuation. Several passengers sustained minor injuries during the chaotic scene, with the NTSB now reviewing the evacuation response.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/horrifying-video-shows-moment-frontier-airlines-plane-hits-person-on-denver-runway/articleshow/131027681.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/horrifying-video-shows-moment-frontier-airlines-plane-hits-person-on-denver-runway/articleshow/131027681.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-12T09:20:48+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131027891,imgsize-5222862.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[HasanAbi loses his cool on Twitch after “white baby” comment sparks heated rant]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131025909.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[HasanAbi sparked major online debate after angrily reacting to a Twitch viewer who called him a “white baby” during a discussion about anti-DEI movements and racism. The political streamer defended his comments by stressing his experiences as a Muslim American facing discrimination and rejected claims that he was being anti-Asian. Clips from the livestream quickly spread online, with viewers divided over whether Hasan’s emotional response was justified or an overreaction to a joke.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/hasanabi-loses-his-cool-on-twitch-after-white-baby-comment-sparks-heated-rant/articleshow/131025909.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/hasanabi-loses-his-cool-on-twitch-after-white-baby-comment-sparks-heated-rant/articleshow/131025909.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-12T05:40:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131025909,imgsize-39434.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["Before Charlie was assassinated....": Candace Owens dragged into online conspiracy storm involving Charlie Kirk, Erika Kirk and Dan Bilzerian]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131025887.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens is facing fresh online controversy after a viral social media post linked her to Dan Bilzerian while referencing Charlie Kirk, Erika Kirk and Ben Shapiro. The post made several unverified allegations and reignited debate around Owens’ past interactions with Bilzerian, including resurfaced comments about private text messages. While no evidence has supported the claims spreading online, the controversy has fuelled intense speculation, backlash and political infighting across social media platforms.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/before-charlie-was-assassinated-candace-owens-dragged-into-online-conspiracy-storm-involving-charlie-kirk-erika-kirk-and-dan-bilzerian/articleshow/131025887.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/before-charlie-was-assassinated-candace-owens-dragged-into-online-conspiracy-storm-involving-charlie-kirk-erika-kirk-and-dan-bilzerian/articleshow/131025887.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-12T05:15:38+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131025887,imgsize-29608.cms"/></item></channel></rss>